            <div class="col-md-2"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="row tech-header">
            <div class="col-md-12 centralize">
              <h3 class="flat-font"><%= "The latest generation of tunable white LED lighting" %></h3>
            </div>
          </div>


          <div class="row tech-content">
            <div class="col-md-12">
               <p>Aurora’s LUNA Colour Xchange, or LUNAcx, line features colour temperature adjustment (CTA) lighting technology to allow the creation of application-specific environments. Through the use of a dedicated LUNAcx control unit, lamp brightness and colour temperature can be altered simultaneously or independently, from a warm 3000K, to a neutral 4000K, to a cool 6400K. </p>
              
            </div>
          </div>


          <div class="row tech-header">
            <div class="col-md-12 centralize">
              <h3 class="flat-font"><%= "How does LUNAcx work?" %></h3>
            </div>
          </div>

           <div class="row tech-content">
            <div class="col-md-12">
               <p>The change of colour temperature and light intensity is achieved by mixing the light output of two groups of LEDs. One group has a warm colour temperature and the other has a cool colour temperature. Changing the light output of these two groups allows to colour temperature to vary seamlessly between these two values. </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row tech-pictures">
            <div class="col-md-12 centralize">
              <figure>
                <%=image_tag("lunacx/circadian-rhythm.png", :class=>"img-responsive")%>
                <figcaption><b>Did you know?</b> Daylight has the ability to invigorate and even heal because of the power it has over circadian rhythm. Once the sun goes down, it cues our bodies to begin preparing for sleep, which involves lowering body temperature, producing melatonin, and decreasing cortisol levels. Once the sun rises, the process reverses and our bodies prepare the face the day.</figcaption>
              </figure>  
            </div>
          </div>


          <div class="row tech-header">
            <div class="col-md-12 centralize">
              <h3 class="flat-font"><%= "Enhance any space" %></h3>
            </div>
          </div>

           <div class="row tech-content">
            <div class="col-md-12">
               <p>LUNAcx is ideal for offices, retail, residential and hospitality applications. The right colour temperature at the right time has the power to increase productivity and even alter mood. For instance, incorporating high colour temperatures, 5000K to 6500K, can help suppress melatonin and raise alertness in a work environment. Dimming and adjusting the lights to a warm 3000K in a restaurant adds an ambiance of relaxation and comfort, setting the tone for an enjoyable meal. Plus, up to 100 downlights can be interconnected and controlled, making LUNAcx ideal for retail spaces.</p>
            </div>
          </div>



        </div><!-- container -->
      </div>
    </div>
